@CarManaagementApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5233
@AuthToken = replace-with-token

### Login
POST {{CarManaagementApi_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "admin",
  "password": "admin",
  "rememberMe": true
}

### Auth Me
GET {{CarManaagementApi_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

### Lookups Enums
GET {{CarManaagementApi_HostAddress}}/api/v1/lookups/enums
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

### Cars Browse
GET {{CarManaagementApi_HostAddress}}/api/v1/cars?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

### Create Booking
POST {{CarManaagementApi_HostAddress}}/api/v1/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "CUS-1001",
  "carId": "CAR-1001",
  "locationCode": "PNQ",
  "pickAt": "2026-03-10T10:00:00Z",
  "dropAt": "2026-03-12T10:00:00Z",
  "dailyPrice": 2700,
  "notes": "Airport pickup"
}

### Dashboard Summary
GET {{CarManaagementApi_HostAddress}}/api/v1/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}
